{"tid":1511421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人人皆可做] 唔好以為Twitter個檢舉係廢，雖遠必誅，毒撚救世界","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T08:21:13.000Z","uid":138608,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"078b4077edcd8124a92b43c76f1eab906353452b","tid":1511421,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:02:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">tl,dr: Twitter Report冇Facebook咁揸流灘, 樓主 3日一件五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有ac 嘅要檢舉, 已有N年ac嘅更加要</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前言：</span><br />\n眾所鳩知，外國人比我地更加多用Twitter<br />\n其實Twitter個介面十分易用，比起Facebook更加簡單。<br />\n事源小弟一向睇開日本囡囡，個Twitter account 都有返咁上下年資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遇到中国五毛抹黑前線義士做非人生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲要配張圖係前線手足舉美國旗<br />\n我真係覺得好噁心，即刻檢舉佢老母同佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有關嘅tweet(twitter嘅post)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>慎入</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日：</span><br />\n正當我以為Twitter同Facebook一樣，放哂風Ban咗幾百ac就當冇事嘅時候，<br />\n我突然收到個通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PbyAvPh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPbyAvPh.png&h=45a96aa3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以見到個tweet係24號先出，而我係25號凌晨瞓唔著見到先report，27號收到通知<br />\n而根據ac 主人之後嘅tweet，雖然冇BAN到但已經有所限制同應該俾twitter 睇撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點：<br />\n1. Twitter 嘅檢舉回應, 唔會hea 鳩我, 但未會Ban 人ac<br />\n2. 樓主推測可能係因為得我一個人檢舉, 所以淨係將條五毛放入監察名單到, 冇Ban到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 大家應該開咗Twitter ac, 但毒撚可能有3年或以上年資, 可能會納入考慮因素 (唔係bot)[/b]</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n各位，Twitter檢舉唔難，有細緻分類，請大家睇到仆街留言要檢舉，尤其是不實言論同侮辱性言論，可能差你一個留言就Ban ac ![/b]</span></span>"},{"pid":"999d7bfb32d4664db396e0372ba3a70945773392","tid":1511421,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:02:23.000Z","msg":"自推十連1/10"},{"pid":"42d8f69872cc57303cf4eb713f788286b51886d4","tid":1511421,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"自推十連2/10"},{"pid":"67a29f7f30bf80aa70268451b43ef4d1d849dfc5","tid":1511421,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:02:57.000Z","msg":"自推十連3/10"},{"pid":"a6d86299da6ab146b0262162470688942435e1dc","tid":1511421,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:03:14.000Z","msg":"自推十連4/10"},{"pid":"305efea962514b2234cd1f5220c55c67f7924c94","tid":1511421,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"自推十連5/10"},{"pid":"81272952dfb456f453cfa6ba94e7e7b3be896dd7","tid":1511421,"uid":312348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8715ac0e948b358b36b6506018c9740aca9264","tid":1511421,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:03:47.000Z","msg":"自推十連6/10"},{"pid":"c2d7e65ef1d0192e4c0e4c93b52714671f9e2a33","tid":1511421,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019